Class Set

Direct Known Subclasses:
SortedSet
public class Set
extends ODMGCollection
implements Set, org.odmg.DSet

A persistent wrapper for a java.util.Set. The underlying collection is a HashSet.

Author:
Gavin King
See Also:
HashSet, Serialized Form
